content.rendered:
Directed by Venkat Prabhu

Written by Venkat Prabhu. K. Chandru. Ezhilarasu Gunasekaran

Cast Silambarasan Rajendar (Abdul Khaaliq). S.J. Suryah (Dhanushkodi). Kalyani Priyadarshan (Seetha Lakshmi). S.A. Chandrashekhar (Arivazhagan). Anjena Kirti (Zarina Begum (as Anjena Kriti)). Y.G. Mahendran (Paranthaaman). Daniel Annie Pope (Rafique). Chandrasekhar (Tamizhvaanan). Karunakaran (Syed Baasha). Premgi Amaren (Eeswara Moorthy). Manoj K. Bharathi (John (as Manoj Bharatiraaja)). Aravind Akash (Hitman). Subbu Panchu (Mugilan). Mahat Raghavendra (Traffic Police)

Language Tamil

Producers Suresh Kamatchi.

Production V House Productions.
